{"tid":1577083,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[慎入有圖] 呢隻咩黎","createTime":"2019-09-17T13:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T14:09:05.000Z","uid":244375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"12e94570f61fce0051402e4d6500d3569c4a0e9c","tid":1577083,"uid":244375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tic1gE1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftic1gE1.png&h=0af770a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"329b12aed6e99ac8bd653e96acd3cb8470b161d0","tid":1577083,"uid":58630,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:52:05.000Z","msg":"香港警察"},{"pid":"07f0f1404d910b20393f92444dc8a7edaa97007d","tid":1577083,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:52:43.000Z","msg":"開啟新戰線：「天滅中共 平反六四」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正式輸出革命<br />\n<br />\n係大陸人比較多嘅地方，<br />\neg. ifc國歌集會，上水羅湖落馬洲邊境，大學內地生（NDS) 聚腳場合<br />\n<br />\n1）不斷傳播解放軍89六四當年鎮壓市民真相<br />\n<br />\n2）瘋狂播《血染的風采》，播到中共連每日150單程證都唔夠膽放落嚟為止，彭麗媛版本更理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3）要將「天滅中共，平反六四」加入為一主要口號，用國語讀更佳<br />\n（如果見到啲廢老藍絲拍片最好叫呢句，啲官媒一定唔夠膽將啲片傳返上大陸，要令佢哋嘅維穩工作白做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utvG-uwDsD8&amp;list=RDutvG-uwDsD8&amp;start_radio=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DutvG-uwDsD8%26list%3DRDutvG-uwDsD8%26start_radio%3D1&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5JS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=17fc4723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utvG-uwDsD8&amp;list=RDutvG-uwDsD8&amp;start_radio=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n也許我告別 將不再回來 你是否理解 你是否明白<br />\n也許我倒下 再不能起來 你是否還要 永久的期待<br />\n<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的旗幟上有我們血染的風采<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的旗幟上有我們血染的風采<br />\n<br />\n也許我的眼睛 再不能睜開 你是否理解 我沉默的情懷<br />\n也許我長眠 將不能醒來 你是否相信 我化作了山脈<br />\n<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的土壤裡有我們付出的愛<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的土壤裡有我們付出的愛<br />\n<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的旗幟上有我們血染的風采<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的旗幟上有我們血染的風采<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果有人話：「呢啲係鄰國嘅事，我哋顧掂自己香港，爭取真普選先」<br />\n請你哋block Q咗呢啲人，果啲係五毛嚟<br />\n因為而家係鄰國過去咁多年每日每分每秒搞鳩緊我哋<br />\n<br />\n鄰國愈亂，自顧不暇，各省地方勢力掘起，對我哋有利</strong></span>"},{"pid":"8a2c40a55fb94185e681d6fa91a47e69100ccaf1","tid":1577083,"uid":249480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:53:25.000Z","msg":"草蜢？"},{"pid":"599fad695e37b080bfdefb9d5c87e96adcbe0f22","tid":1577083,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:53:55.000Z","msg":"當popo咁打死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6562dbeb947f2a019545d95b447270749b7dea","tid":1577083,"uid":220368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJFNWKk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtJFNWKk.jpg&h=f041e3f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dc6a1980293028a24256857fa55cd41ee306b18","tid":1577083,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:09:05.000Z","msg":"冇毒 唔洗驚"}]}